<br>
Triple wield is supposed to be a 50% damage add to each weapons damage. (or basicly a 8.2 damage add) for a while i have not really looked at my triple wield damage because usually it is used in dire emergency where the last thing i am looking at is my damage as it scrolls accors my system chat. <br>
<br>
however i was in a battle the other day and looked back at my damage after the battle and found that where i was doing on average 85- 95 damage (after resists) my Triple Wield was only dont 12 - 14 damage. WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?!?!<br>
<br>
at the very least my TW should be doing 40 - 50 damage add per hit. and since that was 85-95 with about 20% resists i should be doing 50 - 65 per hit. this crapy damage add stayed at 12 - 14 damage no matter if i was hitting a yellow con or a green con. I know for a fact that TW used to do better damage than that.<br>
<br>
While we are on the subject Charge is now a worthless ability. it was stated that charge would be given to us in essance pre-nerfed because mythic would rather give us too little and have to add more than give us to much and have to take it away. but they gave us too little in a 10s sprint then made it worse by giving every one and their mama endo regen. <br>
<br>
